OL,3,CPrincess of Wales' statement in full
OL,5,FThe has revealed she is undergoing
OL,6,Fcancer treatment.
OL,8,FIn a video message released on Friday,
OL,9,FKate said that her abdominal surgery
OL,10,Fin January revealed "cancer had been
OL,11,Fpresent".
OL,13,FShe said that she is now undergoing a
OL,14,Fcourse of preventative chemotherapy,
OL,15,Fand is "getting stronger every day".
OL,17,FHere is her message in full:
