OL,3,CPrincess of Wales' statement in full
OL,5,F"I wanted to take this opportunity to
OL,6,Fsay thank you, personally, for all the
OL,7,Fwonderful messages of support and for
OL,8,Fyour understanding whilst I have been
OL,9,Frecovering from surgery.
OL,11,F"It has been an incredibly tough
OL,12,Fcouple of months for our entire
OL,13,Ffamily, but I've had a fantastic
OL,14,Fmedical team who have taken great care
OL,15,Fof me, for which I am so grateful.
OL,17,F"In January, I underwent major
OL,18,Fabdominal surgery in London and at the
OL,19,Ftime, it was thought that my condition
OL,20,Fwas non-cancerous.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.!/*%/"-$ /*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,
