OL,3,CPrincess of Wales' statement in full
OL,5,F"The surgery was successful. However,
OL,6,Ftests after the operation found cancer
OL,7,Fhad been present.
OL,9,F"My medical team therefore advised
OL,10,Fthat I should undergo a course of
OL,11,Fpreventative chemotherapy and I am now
OL,12,Fin the early stages of that treatment.
OL,13,F"This of course came as a huge shock,
OL,14,Fand William and I have been doing
OL,15,Feverything we can to process and
OL,16,Fmanage this privately for the sake of
OL,17,Four young family.J"As you can imagine,
OL,18,Fthis has taken time. It has taken me
OL,19,Ftime to recover from major surgery in
OL,20,Forder to start my treatment.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.!/*%/"-$ /*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,
