OL,3,CPrincess of Wales' statement in full
OL,5,F"But, most importantly, it has taken
OL,6,Fus time to explain everything to
OL,7,FGeorge, Charlotte and Louis in a way
OL,8,Fthat is appropriate for them, and to
OL,9,Freassure them that I am going to be
OL,10,Fok.J"As I have said to them; I am well
OL,11,Fand getting stronger every day by
OL,12,Ffocusing on the things that will help
OL,13,Fme heal; in my mind, body and spirits.
OL,14,F"Having William by my side is a great
OL,15,Fsource of comfort and reassurance too.
OL,16,FAs is the love, support and kindness
OL,17,Fthat has been shown by so many of you.
OL,18,FIt means so much to us both.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/5
