OL,3,CPrincess of Wales' statement in full
OL,5,F"We hope that you will understand
OL,6,Fthat, as a family, we now need some
OL,7,Ftime, space and privacy while I
OL,8,Fcomplete my treatment. My work has
OL,9,Falways brought me a deep sense of joy
OL,10,Fand I look forward to being back when
OL,11,FI am able, but for now I must focus on
OL,12,Fmaking a full recovery.
OL,14,F"At this time, I am also thinking of
OL,15,Fall those whose lives have been
OL,16,Faffected by cancer.
OL,18,F"For everyone facing this disease, in
OL,19,Fwhatever form, please do not lose
OL,20,Ffaith or hope. You are not alone."
